<blockquote><p>迷思五：性教育只是老师的事？<br>
快问快答：学校性教育授课时数仍不足！家庭是每个孩子「第一个」学习场域，在家落实性教育，很重要！</p></blockquote>
<a href="https://pansci.asia/archives/189143/050_%e6%96%b9%e5%9c%969-1"><img width="1024" height="1024" src="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/78643e66b107864a749e0802b2d426de.png" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="" srcset="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/78643e66b107864a749e0802b2d426de.png 1024w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/78643e66b107864a749e0802b2d426de-150x150.png 150w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/78643e66b107864a749e0802b2d426de-350x350.png 350w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/78643e66b107864a749e0802b2d426de-768x768.png 768w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/78643e66b107864a749e0802b2d426de-560x560.png 560w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/78643e66b107864a749e0802b2d426de-30x30.png 30w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"></a>
