<li>余坤煌（1996）。国小学童家长性知识、性态度及对性教育看法之研究。台湾性学学刊，2（1），11-24。</li>
<li>LARSSON, I., &amp; SVEDIN, C. G. (2001).SEXUAL BEHAVIOUR IN SWEDISH PRESCHOOL CHILDREN, AS OBSERVED BY THEIR PARENTS.ACTA PAEDIATRICA, 90(4), 436-444.</li>
</ol><p>本文与<a href="https://chickensoupfamily.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">鸡汤来了</a>同步刊登，原文为<a href="https://chickensoupfamily.com/2020/07/10/family-sex-education/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">家庭中为何不谈性？3 个「家庭性教育」入门策略</a></p>
